PLAYER STATS HELP
CONSTITUTION
Constitution(CON): Right now, constitution is one of the most important stats on the mud. It is a measure of your general toughness and has a direct impact on not only your hit points but on your endurance and on how much food you can eat before you are full. 

See also: ~CREFstats, strength, dexterity, speed, willpower, intelligence, empathy, charisma
